SQL_STMT_U.val:
select mqdt_admno, mqdt_clntno, clnt110_name1, mqdt_letter, count(*)
from :1/mqdt join :1/clnt on mqdt_admno = clnt101_admno and mqdt_clntno = clnt102_clntno
where mqdt_mqty_id = :2 :3 :4 :5 :6 :7 :8
group by mqdt_admno, mqdt_clntno, clnt110_name1, mqdt_letter
order by mqdt_clntno
for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
